---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'May 14, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | alot.capital"
  description="How A Lot of Land LLC collects, uses, and protects your information at alot.capital."
>
  <section class="section bg-bg-dark !pt-12 md:!pt-20">
    <div class="container-narrow max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white leading-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="prose-content space-y-8 text-white/85 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            This site (alot.capital) is operated by A Lot of Land LLC ("we", "us"), a Tennessee limited liability company. For questions about this policy, email <a href="mailto:David@alot.capital" class="text-gold hover:underline">David@alot.capital</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">What we collect</h2>
          <p>We collect only the information you give us directly:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2 text-white/80">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Free-guide form:</strong> your first name and email address.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Investor application form:</strong> your name, email address, and phone number.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Server logs:</strong> standard technical information (IP address, browser type, pages visited) collected by our hosting provider, Netlify, for security and performance.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not knowingly collect information from anyone under 18.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">How we use it</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-white/80">
            <li>Send you the guide you requested and occasional related updates.</li>
            <li>Review and respond to your investor application.</li>
            <li>Notify you of investment opportunities that match your stated interests.</li>
            <li>Improve the site and its content.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your information with third parties for their own marketing. Ever.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Who processes your data on our behalf</h2>
          <p>We rely on a small set of trusted service providers:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2 text-white/80">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Netlify</strong> — website hosting and form submission storage.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Google Workspace</strong> — email hosting for the David@alot.capital address.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Calendly</strong> — appointment booking (if you schedule a call).</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Each provider has its own privacy policy and processes data only as needed to provide the service to us.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Cookies and analytics</h2>
          <p>
            This site uses minimal cookies. If we enable analytics, we use privacy-respecting tools that do not track you across other sites. We do not use cookies for advertising.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You can, at any time:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2 text-white/80">
            <li>Ask what personal information we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Ask us to correct or delete it.</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from any email we send (link at the bottom of every message).</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for future marketing communications.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Send any request to <a href="mailto:David@alot.capital" class="text-gold hover:underline">David@alot.capital</a> and we'll act on it within 30 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">How we secure it</h2>
          <p>
            Your data is transmitted over HTTPS and stored on infrastructure with industry-standard security controls. No online service is 100% secure, but we take reasonable measures to protect what you share.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be posted here with a new "Last updated" date. Continued use of the site after a change means you accept the update.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-3">Not investment advice</h2>
          <p>
            This site is for informational purposes only and is not an offer to sell or a solicitation to buy any security. Investments in real estate carry risk, including loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
